HEADWORD: Vinometer
<hw>Vin*om"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>vinum</ets> vine + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument for
